        <title>CTRL &#43; U</title>
        <link>https://saipheblue.github.io/p/ctrl--u/</link>
        <pubDate>Tue, 11 Feb 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
        
        <guid>https://saipheblue.github.io/p/ctrl--u/</guid>
        <description>&lt;img src="https://saipheblue.github.io/p/ctrl--u/1.png" alt="Featured image of post CTRL &#43; U" /&gt;&lt;h2 id=&#34;keyboard-shortcut&#34;&gt;Keyboard Shortcut
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;code&gt;CTRL + U&lt;/code&gt; clears all inputs from text fields, for example, when entering a username or password. No need to select everything and delete it or smash the backspace key.&lt;/p&gt;
